query:
SELECT 
  pwi.id,
  pwi.waveId,
  pwi.status,
  pwi.pickedQuantity,
  pwi.totalQuantity,
  pw.status as wave_status
FROM pickingWaveItems pwi
INNER JOIN pickingWaves pw ON pwi.waveId = pw.id
WHERE pw.status = 'completed'
ORDER BY pwi.id;
